Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（美國總統聲明不排除武力介入）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳認為人的意念\N可以改變命運嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請妳盡量做到\N妳現在能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.38,0:02:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第19話 心之迷宮\N地震還真多耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第19話 心之迷宮\N富士山好像爆發了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界似乎要毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是熱心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該又要去醫院了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎每天都去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望月醫生在問\N巧海那件事情怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能幫我傳話\N說我明天會讓他過去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人果然是那種關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯雖然一副很排斥的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯在自暴自棄的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆也是一直陪在他身邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自暴自棄？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒聽說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯他啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主將…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯，我來找你要答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的眼神又凶悍起來了喔，命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在國中的時候\N似乎是劍道社的強者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊，在全國大賽之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習的時候左膝蓋受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經過一段時間之後\N他的傷幾乎已經痊癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是似乎完全失去幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一陣子非常自暴自棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候…他有點可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到他被學生會找去為止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，就算楯因此被大家疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是詩帆還是\N拼命地不斷鼓勵他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在楯的態度\N也就很可以理解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"加油吧"這種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是說的人還是聽的人\N都很不負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，妳說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有，沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會一輩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有辦法走路了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從弄傷膝蓋之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在迷惘\N自己究竟該怎麼做才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，我覺得我非得陪著她不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了誰做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼而負責
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話聽起來很冠冕堂皇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這真的是你的願望嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能夠對你在國中時代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上一切的這把竹劍發誓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把道場上你的名牌拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，主將…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，原來妳在啊，雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為我找妳幾次了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機沒開機喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騷擾簡訊？給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫妳把發送人找出來\N教訓他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不，沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去找巧海嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每次面臨抉擇時\N就會畏畏縮縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得拉著他走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，你為什麼不去醫院？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從媽媽過世後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，當我的身高逐漸追上她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後像這樣跟她分開住之後\N我才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的讓姊姊很勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我是多麼依賴她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到國外接受手術得花很多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊不但把房子賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還為了獎學金而轉學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後每天打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣還是不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術的成功機率也沒有很高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是失敗的話\N欠的債還是照樣存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真的有必要為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到這種地步嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過姊姊卻總是笑口常開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那樣我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我覺得很沈重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還是個男人\N就去動手術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到徹底恢復健康之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己在短時間內\N把那些債都還清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姊不也是希望你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以什麼話都沒說\N而不斷努力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是HiME的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，你不准笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真驚訝，原來晶是HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶是HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很沈重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有必要活下去嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，晶是女生啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，真是嚇到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶是女生，是HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後跟巧海感情很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微讓我一個人靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊最大障礙的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天先到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳睡得挺熟的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…不知不覺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾到臉了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近妳是不是把自己\N逼得太緊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了借妳那個以外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有什麼能幫得上忙的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，不過我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，打擾妳工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無時無刻都在擔心妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點，請妳別忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳，別太深入我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖…玖我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真，真巧啊…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣!笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣好生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到她那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不明白詳細情形如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果妳真的重視舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要為她做點事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能盡量去做\N妳能做到的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N妳的想法一定可以傳達給她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，我去試試看!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人果然很像兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之啊\N你還是去跟你姊談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姊一定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然隨便動別人的東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你看到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎？巧海!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海!巧海!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全…搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過姊姊卻總是笑口常開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那樣我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我覺得很沈重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我只能這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能笑著面對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子做錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶被打倒的話，巧海會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很沈重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（妳最弱）\N（所以第一個找上妳）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（珠洲城會消失）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（打倒妳 打倒妳 打倒妳）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（妳最弱，所以第一個找上妳）\N（珠洲城會消失，打倒妳…）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黛安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之，妳聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭姑息和卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都要正正當當的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳如果是我的搭檔\N就要記住這點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守護舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人就非得打倒不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳，原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人威脅我，說要打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把小遙消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，如果我能監視舞衣\N並且打倒妳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過妳多少次\N叫妳不可以動手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連妳\N也不肯聽我的話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我喜歡舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳為什麼能\N對雪之做出那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是也說過喜歡雪之嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很沈重…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一個人看的很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有多辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有多難受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳根本就不懂!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有妳在\N一切都變得亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還好沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何會讓你擔心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為了我忍耐很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的時候還要勉強自己笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再欺騙自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，我問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊真正想要的東西是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然迷惘了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我現在想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會自己一個人到美國去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受手術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經可以自己走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想靠自己的力量前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以姊姊妳也為了自己而活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為妳自己而活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子，真是太好了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海會去動手術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要為了我，而是為了妳自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再…再也不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我根本搞不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽舞衣的興趣是打工
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅長燒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巧海的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正想要的東西是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是能夠到外面比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是去快餐店吃了一客聖代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真容易滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟哥哥一起\N什麼東西都好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下\N小的還真是誠惶誠恐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，無須緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥對人家好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為覺得人家會受傷\N都是自己害的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要哥哥真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你虛情假意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你只要看著我就好，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊真正想要的東西是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的失去一切了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.94,0:22:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:23:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊很沈重…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我變胖了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊真正想要的東西是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，我能體會妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聽的人可是很痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之舞 淚之命運

Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:23:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們會相遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一族從很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就跟HiME的戰爭有所關連
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以老爸才叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱瞞自己女孩子的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.65,0:24:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候不禁會想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我真的是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就能以\N彼此都是男生的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當好朋友\N而有更深一層的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.96,0:24:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.23,0:24:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是一個普通女生的身份\N跟你相遇會怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.60,0:24:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.57,0:24:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.94,0:24:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是HiME呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.88,0:24:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會對你這麼地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動心了呢


